  </p>
  <p
    className="info"
  >
    You can also import results from an InterProScan run (JSON format) to visualise hits in the sequence context.
  </p>
  <Memo(Loadable)
    data={
      {
        "description": "The status of all the requested InterProScan searches",
        "name": "Your InterProScan searches",
      }
    }
    processData={[Function]}
  />
  <div
    className="button-bar"
  >
    <div
      className="button-group"
    >
      <GoToNewSearch />
